# Edit this site (your control panel)

## The only files you need day-to-day

1) **Homepage content**
- `index.md`

2) **Site settings (name, affiliation, links, favicon/avatar paths)**
- `_config.yml`

3) **Design (font, background, colors, spacing)**
- `assets/css/style.scss`

4) **Layout (left panel structure, header/footer)**
- `_layouts/homepage.html`

## Quick links (open these in GitHub)
- [index.md](./index.md)
- [_config.yml](./_config.yml)
- [style.scss](./assets/css/style.scss)
- [homepage layout](./_layouts/homepage.html)
- [images folder](./assets/img/)
- [files folder (CV etc.)](./assets/files/)

## Notes
- Ignore everything else unless we explicitly decide to change it.
